@tag
Feature: Diageo Web Application Login
  User want to be able to login with valid credentials.
  User should not be logged in with invalid credentials.

  @DiageoURL
  Scenario: User should be directed to log in page
    Given User is administrator.
    When User clicks clicks on URL:https://staging.diageo.trutags.dev/login
    Then User should be able to be directed to a log in page
 
  @DiageoLogin
  Scenario: User should be able to log in.
    Given I click url: https://staging.diageo.trutags.dev/login
    And The log in page displays.
    When User enter email address.
    And User enter password.
    And User click on the LOGIN button
    Then I should be logged in.
    And Diageo dashboard opens. 


